title: 12/31/20 – HOUR 1 – Should the Dolphins move off T’ua?
itunes:title: 12/31/20 – HOUR 1 – Should the Dolphins move off T’ua?
description:
Doug Gottlieb and Rob Parker fill in for Dan Patrick and question if the Miami Dolphins are sold on their rookie quarterback T’ua Tagovailoa. They explain which college football team has the most to prove in tomorrow’s playoff games and applaud the San Diego Padres for making big moves while everyone else is standing pat.
